      <h1 class='title'>Community Health Councils</h1>
    </div>
    <div class='commons-written-statements-sitting' id='content'>
      
      <cite class='section'>HC Deb 16 September 2004 vol 424 cc1750-1WS</cite>
      <a class='permalink column-permalink' id='column_1751ws' title='Col. 1751WS &mdash; HC Deb 16 September 2004 vol 424 c1751WS' name='column_1751ws' href='#column_1751ws' rel='bookmark'>1751WS</a>
      <div class='hentry member_contribution'>
        <a name='S6CV0424P2_20040916_CWS2_566'>  </a>
        <blockquote cite='http://hansard.millbanksystems.com/people/mr-peter-bottomley' class='contribution_text entry-content'>
          <a class='speech-permalink permalink' href='#S6CV0424P2_20040916_CWS2_566' title='Link to this speech by Mr Peter Bottomley' rel='bookmark'>&sect;</a>
          <cite class='member author entry-title'><a href="/people/mr-peter-bottomley" title="Mr Peter Bottomley">Peter Bottomley</a></cite>
          <p class="first-para">To ask the Secretary of State for Health who devised the community health councils' replacement systems. [188238]</p>
        </blockquote>
      </div>
      
      <div class='hentry member_contribution'>
        <a name='S6CV0424P2_20040916_CWS2_567'>  </a>
        <blockquote cite='http://hansard.millbanksystems.com/people/ms-rosie-winterton' class='contribution_text entry-content'>
          <a class='speech-permalink permalink' href='#S6CV0424P2_20040916_CWS2_567' title='Link to this speech by Ms Rosie Winterton' rel='bookmark'>&sect;</a>
          <cite class='member author entry-title'><a href="/people/ms-rosie-winterton" title="Ms Rosie Winterton">Ms Rosie Winterton</a></cite>
          <p class="first-para">The arrangements that have replaced community health councils were developed by the Government in consultation with the public, parliamentarians, the national health service, the voluntary sector and many more interested stakeholders.</p>
        </blockquote>
      </div>
      
      <div class='hentry member_contribution'>
        <a name='S6CV0424P2_20040916_CWS2_568'>  </a>
        <blockquote cite='http://hansard.millbanksystems.com/people/mr-peter-bottomley' class='contribution_text entry-content'>
          <a class='speech-permalink permalink' href='#S6CV0424P2_20040916_CWS2_568' title='Link to this speech by Mr Peter Bottomley' rel='bookmark'>&sect;</a>
          <cite class='member author entry-title'><a href="/people/mr-peter-bottomley" title="Mr Peter Bottomley">Peter Bottomley</a></cite>
          <p class="first-para">To ask the Secretary of State for Health when he expects to publish an assessment of the benefits of replacing community health councils. [188239]</p>
        </blockquote>
      </div>
      
      <div class='hentry member_contribution'>
        <a name='S6CV0424P2_20040916_CWS2_569'>  </a>
        <blockquote cite='http://hansard.millbanksystems.com/people/ms-rosie-winterton' class='contribution_text entry-content'>
          <a class='speech-permalink permalink' href='#S6CV0424P2_20040916_CWS2_569' title='Link to this speech by Ms Rosie Winterton' rel='bookmark'>&sect;</a>
          <cite class='member author entry-title'><a href="/people/ms-rosie-winterton" title="Ms Rosie Winterton">Ms Rosie Winterton</a></cite>
